There was also many waves that allowed everyone to make profit multiple times . Overall it was a great pump as we managed to maintain top position on Binance_CEX for 22 minutes . If we had not been faced with that amount of sell pressure , we could have defintely hit 200 % + . Thank you all for participating , we have something big to announce really soon that everyone will want to stick around for as well , stay tuned !
